ActNational Defence Act
PrecisAppointment of CAROLINE MAYNARD of Ottawa, Ontario, as interim Chairperson of the Military Grievances External Review Committee, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of one year or until such time as a Chairperson of the Military Grievances External Review Committee is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective January 4, 2017.
